<br>
A very optimistic estimate is 3-4 hours. Here's the breakdown:<br>
Isle 1: 1 hr (Buying coffins, buffing, fight, rebuffing for isle 2). Notice that you can always buy the key to the 2nd island from the dwarven vendor. However, since the key is expensive and the fight is reasonably easy, most people choose to fight.<br>
Isle 2: Less than an hour<br>
Isle 3: 1 hr without clearing the entire island<br>
